{"id":190,"parent_id":186,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":190,"title":"Philippians 4","subtitle":"","short_title":"Philip.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 4"],[".studySummary",["i","Stand fast in the Lord—We believe in being honest, true, and chaste."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.1","order":"03.13.004.20826"},["b","1"],"Therefore, my brethren dearly beloved and longed for, my joy and crown, so",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"stand fast"],"in the Lord,",["i","my"],"dearly beloved."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.2","order":"03.13.004.20827"},["b","2"],"I beseech Euodias, and beseech Syntyche, that they be of the same mind in the Lord."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.3","order":"03.13.004.20828"},["b","3"],"And I entreat thee also, true",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"yokefellow"],", help those women which laboured with me in the gospel, with Clement also, and",["i","with"],"other my fellowlabourers, whose names",["i","are"],"in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"book of life"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.4","order":"03.13.004.20829"},["b","4"],"Rejoice in the Lord alway:",["i","and"],"again I say, Rejoice."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.5","order":"03.13.004.20830"},["b","5"],"Let your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"moderation"],"be known unto all men. The Lord",["i","is"],"at hand."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.6","order":"03.13.004.20831"},["b","6"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"Be"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"careful"],"for nothing; but in every thing by",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"prayer"],"and supplication with",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_6d"},"thanksgiving"],"let your requests be made known unto God."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.7","order":"03.13.004.20832"},["b","7"],"And the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"peace"],"of God, which passeth all",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"understanding"],", shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"keep"],"your hearts and minds through Christ Jesus."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.8","order":"03.13.004.20833"},["b","8"],"Finally, brethren, whatsoever things are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"true"],", whatsoever things",["i","are"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"honest"],", whatsoever things",["i","are"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"just"],", whatsoever things",["i","are"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_8d"},"pure"],", whatsoever things",["i","are"],["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_8e"},"lovely"],",",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_8f"},"whatsoever"],"things",["i","are"],"of good report; if",["i","there be"],"any",["sup","g"],["a",{"href":"fn_8g"},"virtue"],", and if",["i","there be"],"any praise,",["sup","h"],["a",{"href":"fn_8h"},"think"],"on these things."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.9","order":"03.13.004.20834"},["b","9"],"Those things, which ye have both learned, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"received"],", and heard, and seen in me, do: and the God of peace shall be with you."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.10","order":"03.13.004.20835"},["b","10"],"But I rejoiced in the Lord greatly, that now at the last your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"care"],"of me hath flourished again; wherein ye were also careful, but ye",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"lacked"],"opportunity."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.11","order":"03.13.004.20836"},["b","11"],"Not that I speak in respect of want: for I have learned, in whatsoever state I am,",["i","therewith"],"to be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"content"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.12","order":"03.13.004.20837"},["b","12"],"I know both how to be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"abased"],", and I know how to abound: every where and in all things I am instructed both to be full and to be hungry, both to abound and to suffer need."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.13","order":"03.13.004.20838"},["b","13"],"I can do all things through",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"Christ"],"which",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"strengtheneth"],"me."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.14","order":"03.13.004.20839"},["b","14"],"Notwithstanding ye have well done, that ye did",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"communicate"],"with my affliction."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.15","order":"03.13.004.20840"},["b","15"],"Now ye Philippians know also, that in the beginning of the gospel, when I departed from Macedonia, no church communicated with me as concerning giving and receiving, but ye only."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.16","order":"03.13.004.20841"},["b","16"],"For even in Thessalonica ye sent once and again unto my necessity."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.17","order":"03.13.004.20842"},["b","17"],"Not because I desire a gift: but I desire",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"fruit"],"that may abound to your account."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.18","order":"03.13.004.20843"},["b","18"],"But I have all, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"abound"],": I am full, having received of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"Epaphroditus"],"the things",["i","which were sent"],"from you, an odour of a sweet smell, a sacrifice acceptable, wellpleasing to God."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.19","order":"03.13.004.20844"},["b","19"],"But my God shall supply all your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"need"],"according to his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"riches"],"in glory by Christ Jesus."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.20","order":"03.13.004.20845"},["b","20"],"Now unto God and our Father",["i","be"],"glory for ever and ever. Amen."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.21","order":"03.13.004.20846"},["b","21"],"Salute every saint in Christ Jesus. The brethren which are with me greet you."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.22","order":"03.13.004.20847"},["b","22"],"All the saints salute you, chiefly they that are of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"Cæsar’s"],"household."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.23","order":"03.13.004.20848"},["b","23"],"The grace of our Lord Jesus Christ",["i","be"],"with you all. Amen."]],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip.closing.6","order":".000.20915"},[".closing","¶It was written to the Philippians from Rome by Epaphroditus."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.1a","order":"03.13.004.20849"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/10.12"},"1 Cor. 10:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/16.13.13-14"},"16:13 (13–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/5.1"},"Gal. 5:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.27"},"Philip. 1:27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/87.8"},"D&C 87:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.3a","order":"03.13.004.20851"},["b","3a"],["span.small","GR"],"associate."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.3b","order":"03.13.004.20853"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/book-of-life"},"TG Book of Life"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.5a","order":"03.13.004.20855"},["b","5a"],["span.small","GR"],"gentleness.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/modesty"},"TG Modesty"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/temperance"},"Temperance"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.6a","order":"03.13.004.20857"},["b","6a"],["span.small","GR"],"Don’t be unduly concerned about anything."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.6b","order":"03.13.004.20859"},["b","6b"],["span.small","JST"],"Philip. 4:6 …",["i","afflicted"],"…",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/55.22"},"Ps. 55:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/16.3"},"Prov. 16:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/6.25"},"Matt. 6:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.6c","order":"03.13.004.20861"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prayer"},"TG Prayer"],"."],["div",{"id":"6d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.6d","order":"03.13.004.20863"},["b","6d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/thanksgiving"},"TG Thanksgiving"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.7a","order":"03.13.004.20865"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peace-of-god"},"TG Peace of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.7b","order":"03.13.004.20867"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/understanding"},"TG Understanding"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.7c","order":"03.13.004.20869"},["b","7c"],["span.small","GR"],"guard."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.8a","order":"03.13.004.20871"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/truth"},"TG Truth"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.8b","order":"03.13.004.20873"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/honesty"},"TG Honesty"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.8c","order":"03.13.004.20875"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/righteousness"},"TG Righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"8d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.8d","order":"03.13.004.20877"},["b","8d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/purity"},"TG Purity"],"."],["div",{"id":"8e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.8e","order":"03.13.004.20879"},["b","8e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/beauty"},"TG Beauty"],"."],["div",{"id":"8f","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.8f","order":"03.13.004.20881"},["b","8f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/a-of-f/1.13"},"A of F 1:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"8g","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.8g","order":"03.13.004.20883"},["b","8g"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/chastity"},"TG Chastity"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/virtue"},"Virtue"],"."],["div",{"id":"8h","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.8h","order":"03.13.004.20885"},["b","8h"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/motivations"},"TG Motivations"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/study"},"Study"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.9a","order":"03.13.004.20887"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.1"},"1 Thes. 4:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.10a","order":"03.13.004.20889"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/11.9"},"2 Cor. 11:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.10b","order":"03.13.004.20891"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.30.25,30"},"Philip. 2:30 (25, 30)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.11a","order":"03.13.004.20893"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/contentment"},"TG Contentment"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.12a","order":"03.13.004.20895"},["b","12a"],["span.small","GR"],"humble.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/self-sacrifice"},"TG Self-Sacrifice"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.13a","order":"03.13.004.20897"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/15.5.4-5"},"John 15:5 (4–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.13b","order":"03.13.004.20899"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-tim/1.12"},"1 Tim. 1:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/26.12.11-13"},"Alma 26:12 (11–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.14a","order":"03.13.004.20901"},["b","14a"],["span.small","GR"],"participate."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.17a","order":"03.13.004.20903"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.28.25-28"},"Rom. 15:28 (25–28)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/titus/3.14"},"Titus 3:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.18a","order":"03.13.004.20905"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/9.8"},"2 Cor. 9:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.18b","order":"03.13.004.20907"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.25.25-30"},"Philip. 2:25 (25–30)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.19a","order":"03.13.004.20909"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/23.1"},"Ps. 23:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.19b","order":"03.13.004.20911"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/treasure"},"TG Treasure"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.22a","order":"03.13.004.20913"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philip/1.13"},"Philip. 1:13"],"."]]}
